# VampireQuery.srv
# Synchronous service for Vampire theorem prover queries
#
# Usage:
#   ros2 service call /vampire/query vampire_bridge/srv/VampireQuery \
#     "{query: {query_type: 'safety', query_name: 'nfz_violation', parameters: ['uav=drone_alpha', 'nfz=zone_1']}}"
#
# Response latency targets:
#   - safety queries: <100ms (p95)
#   - operational queries: <100ms (p95)
#   - planning queries: <200ms (p95)

# Request
vampire_bridge/ReasoningQuery query
---
# Response
vampire_bridge/ReasoningResult result
